This repository is a **GitNodes knowledge base**: a graph of markdown notes with
YAML frontmatter, where Git is the single source of truth. Follow the conventions
in AGENTS.md. Cursor does not read AGENTS.md automatically, so it is imported here.

@AGENTS.md

## Using the knowledge graph

A read-only MCP server named `gitnodes` is configured (see `.cursor/mcp.json`).
Prefer its tools — `search_brain`, `list_nodes`, `read_node`, `node_links` — to
explore the graph instead of grepping blindly. The server never writes; make edits
as ordinary markdown commits, keeping each note's frontmatter valid.
